
Star Slots Dev Log:

NYI: 
transitions for display screen
victory audios
tracking points 
local storage to keep score

functionalities:-------------
calculates value of hit rows and displays it in the info area on the right
misses get reported with "Miss!"
Multiplier x2 if 2 lines hit, x4 for 3 lines, etc. on a power-of basis  2^numLinesHit.
Multiplier added if 2 different kinds of lines hit (e.g. Jacks and Queens) since this can only work absent diagonals and is rarer.
sound plays when each reel stops.

plays a blury screen-tear animation while the reel is spinning
hilights rows that match
grow animation plays on rows that match
"spinning animation" plays in top area after hitting to spin
